      "description": "Mother's Day boosts gifting; cheese sets see peak conversion for last-minute orders.",
      "details": "Mother's Day is the primary seasonal driver for Gardner's Wisconsin Cheese in this window. In 2026, it fell on May 10, creating a significant boost in gifting-intent traffic. Performance peaked with a 3.31× ROAS as high-intent shoppers finalized celebration plans. This seasonal 'halo' often persists for 24 hours as post-holiday 'thank you' gifts are sent.",
